      m_Items:
      - rid: 8544654921302540399
  - m_Id: 2176048618446848
    m_Localized: If this card is in the system, the card on SOCKET {Socket} MUST
      NOT BE {Trait}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 8544654921302540399
  - m_Id: 2176048618446849
    m_Localized: If this card is in the system, there MUST BE a {Trait} card present.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 8544654921302540399
  - m_Id: 2176048618446850
    m_Localized: If this card is in the system, there MUST NOT BE a {Trait} card
      present.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 8544654921302540399
  - m_Id: 2176048618446851
    m_Localized: If this card is in the system, the card to its {Dir} MUST BE {Trait}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 8544654921302540399
  - m_Id: 2176048618446852
    m_Localized: If this card is in the system, the card to its {Dir} MUST NOT BE
